title: Chip Chop
info:
My first ever Atari tune :) I must say it was quite challenging for me to use POKEY chip for the first time in my life. But! It was real fun :) I think I will spawn another .RMT from time to time :)

Percussion sounds taken from "Quickshot" by Michu & 505.
All other sounds made from scratch.

Ranked 4th in ATARI XL/XE POKEY Music Compo at Silly Venture 2013.
